transcripts.text: In your son's job in Ukraine, how is that not a conflict of interest?  It's not a conflict of interest.  There's been no indication of any conflict of interest from Ukraine or anywhere else.  Period.  I'm not going to respond to that.  Let's focus on the problem.  Focus on this man, what he's doing, that no president has ever done.  You're selling access to the president.  You're a damn liar, man.  You said I set up my son to work in an oil company.
Do you think it was wrong for him to take that position, knowing that it was really because that company wanted access to you?
Well, that's not true.  You're saying things you do not know what you're talking about.  No one said that.  Who said that?  Who said that?
